{"id":270323,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-网友13亿公民等赴湖南邵阳探望朱承志遭遣/","date":"2012-12-25T08:45:43Z","modified":"2012-12-25T08:45:43Z","title":"维权网 | 网友13亿公民等赴湖南邵阳探望朱承志遭遣返（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，因为听朱承志妻子说朱承志今天会被释放，网友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民（魏小兵）和醒醒吧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8212;</span><span>辛巴来到湖南邵阳看守所，希望能够见到朱承志。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>来到邵阳看守所，在得知接人意图后，几个警察驱赶他们出大门，并告诉没有上面允许，连给朱承志送钱送物都不行。随后二人被赶来的国保叫到车上约谈，从国保处得知，朱承志</span><span>的案子到今天就结案了，案件已移送至检察院进行起诉，罪名为涉嫌煽动颠覆</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在确认朱承志即将面临审判之后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>亿公民和辛巴通过国保给朱承志存了点钱，然后被国保开车送到火车站离开。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ekaptYMYB-0/UNlK5UOncmI/AAAAAAAAXf8/fA_EiIh82wA/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ekaptYMYB-0/UNlK5UOncmI/AAAAAAAAXf8/fA_EiIh82wA/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"258\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EKKGJGbhPQM/UNlK7EL8mKI/AAAAAAAAXgE/16JExdIpEAk/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"214\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-EKKGJGbhPQM/UNlK7EL8mKI/AAAAAAAAXgE/16JExdIpEAk/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"emai